## Deploy

```bash
cd terraform
terraform init
terraform apply -var image_tag=<your-tag> -var alb_listener_rule_priority=<unique>
```

## Layout

| Path | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `src/` | Express service code |
| `src/lib/auth.ts` | Builds the broker auth middleware from env |
| `src/routes/` | Health, metrics, API routes |
| `policies/` | Cedar `.cedar` policies uploaded by the module |
| `terraform/` | Module call that deploys this service |

## Shadow mode

Set `S2S_SHADOW_MODE=true` to run the inbound auth middleware in log-only mode. Useful when migrating from a legacy auth setup — see `docs/onboarding-existing-app.md` Phase 2b.
